txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Needed: Flawed goo from the insects found within Meluinen. Deliver the items to Thaliollang at Lin Giliath.
'I will begin my studies forthwith, you have my thanks.'
'I wish to study the insects in greater detail. Sometimes they will leave behind a foul smelling residue, a gooey substance. Deliver this to me.'
Elves of Rivendell Task: Flawed Goo
Thaliollang in the Elf-ruin of Meluinen at Lin Giliath requires the return of flawed goo.
Deliver the flawed goo to Thaliollang at Lin Giliath
You are on a task to collect flawed goo from the insects of Meluinen and to deliver them to Thaliollang. Thaliollang can be found at Lin Giliath, the Elf-ruins of Meluinen.
Needed: Flawed goo from the insects found within Meluinen.
